numerous \f(CW\*(C`SSize_t var1 = av_len(var) + 1\*(C'\fR are changed to \f(CW\*(C`size_t var1 = av_len(var) + 1\*(C'\fR as \f(CW\*(C`size_t\*(C'\fR; as the result cannot be negative, in order to expand numerical range
.PP
Addition of \f(CW\*(C`hoa2hoh\*(C'\fR, \f(CW\*(C`binom_test\*(C'\fR, \f(CW\*(C`chunk\*(C'\fR, \f(CW\*(C`get_union\*(C'\fR, \f(CW\*(C`get_unique\*(C'\fR, \f(CW\*(C`Lonly\*(C'\fR, \f(CW\*(C`Ronly\*(C'\fR, \f(CW\*(C`qcut\*(C'\fR, and 3 tukey functions
.PP
Better warnings when non\-array references are given to \f(CW\*(C`intersection\*(C'\fR
.PP
\&\f(CW\*(C`view\*(C'\fR now breaks columns into chunks for very wide data sets, more closely matching R\*(Aqs behavior
.SS 0.18
.IX Subsection "0.18"
\&\f(CW\*(C`restrict\*(C'\fR keyword added to numerous places within \f(CW\*(C`intersection\*(C'\fR to decrease CPU time
.PP
fix to dist.ini for dependencies
